trans-unit.source: Provides helpers for the Visual Basic <see langword="Err" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 为 Visual Basic <see langword="Err" /> 对象提供帮助器。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Information.Err%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 有关详情，请参阅<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Information.Err%2A>。

trans-unit.source: Performs the work for the <see langword="Clear" /> method of the <see langword="Err" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 执行 <see langword="Clear" /> 对象的 <see langword="Err" /> 方法的操作。

trans-unit.source: A helper method.
trans-unit.target: 即帮助器方法。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.ErrObject.Clear%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 有关详情，请参阅<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.ErrObject.Clear%2A>。

trans-unit.source: An integer value that identifies the nature of the error.
trans-unit.target: 标识错误本质的整数值。

trans-unit.source: Visual Basic errors are in the range 0–65535; the range 0–512 is reserved for system errors; the range 513–65535 is available for user-defined errors.
trans-unit.target: Visual Basic 错误处于 0 到 65535 的范围内：范围 0 到 512 保留用于系统错误，范围 513 到 65535 则用于用户定义的错误。

trans-unit.source: Performs the work for the <see langword="Raise" /> method of the <see langword="Err" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 执行 <see langword="Raise" /> 对象的 <see langword="Err" /> 方法的操作。

trans-unit.source: A helper method.
trans-unit.target: 即帮助器方法。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> object.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Exception" /> 对象。

trans-unit.target: 有关详情，请参阅<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.ErrObject.Raise%2A>。

trans-unit.source: Closes all files for the calling assembly and stops the process.
trans-unit.target: 关闭用于调用程序集的所有文件并停止该进程。

trans-unit.source: This class supports the Visual Basic compiler and is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: 此类支持 Visual Basic 编译器，不宜在代码中直接使用。
